<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<Report xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <description
  >Salesperson view: the engagement signals on my open Opportunities where the engaged Contact is NOT on the Deal Team (Match_Path != OCR). These are people marketing/the ecosystem has engaged that I haven't added to OCR yet — the "+ Add" candidates from the panel, in list form, sorted by confidence. Scoped to the running user via &lt;scope&gt;user&lt;/scope&gt;.</description>
    <columns>
        <field>Opportunity_Engagement_Signal__c.Contact__c</field>
    </columns>
    <columns>
